# See https://help.github.com/articles/ignoring-files/ for more about ignoring files.

# dependencies
/node_modules
**/node_modules
/.pnp
.pnp.*
.yarn/*
!.yarn/patches
!.yarn/plugins
!.yarn/releases
!.yarn/versions

# testing
/coverage
/test-results
/playwright-report
/playwright/.cache

# next.js
/.next/
/out/

# production
/build
**/dist

# misc
.DS_Store
*.pem

# debug
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
.pnpm-debug.log*

# env files — never commit real secrets. .env.example IS committed.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# vercel
.vercel

# typescript
*.tsbuildinfo
next-env.d.ts

# local scratch
/tmp
*.local.md

# Claude Code local config (preview launch.json, agent worktrees) — machine-local, not app code.
.claude/

# Spheres source research — scraped wiki HTML + downloaded page assets (bulky, not app code).
# The 6 normalized TSVs ARE versioned (the compendium import source); the raw pages are not.
**/downloaded source web pages/
**/*_SAMPLE.tsv

# PFcore source research — the ~11k-page Archives of Nethys HTML mirror (bulky, not app code).
# The 25 normalized TSVs + parsers + docs in csv/ ARE versioned (the compendium import source).
docs/PFcore Update/**/*.html

# 3pp source research — scraped PoW/Spheres/Akashic/Psionics wiki mirror (bulky, not app
# code). The normalized csv/ (17 TSVs + parsers + manifest) IS versioned — the compendium
# import source, like PFcore Update/csv. (The /* form is required so csv/ can be re-included.)
docs/3pp Update/*
!docs/3pp Update/csv/
**/__pycache__/
